												</tr>
												<tr>
													<td><P class="textNormal"><b>As on October 2009, participation of over 20,000 candidates 
																has been witnessed through various NAC administrations at 14 different states 
																(Rajasthan, Gujarat, Chandigarh, Andhra Pradesh, West Bengal, Orissa, Manipur, 
																Mizoram, Assam, Tripura, Meghalaya, Nagaland, Arunachal Pradesh, Sikkim), which 
																includes tests at some individual colleges/universities as well.</b>
															<br>
															<br>
															The dialogue is on with various other states and the test shall be conducted 
															for them as and when the schedules and timelines are agreed upon. Additionally, 
															any college/university/institute, which is willing to assess <u>at least 1000 
																candidates</u>, can get in direct agreement with NASSCOM and NASSCOM shall 
															organize the test for them.
														</P>
													</td>
												</tr>
