												</tr>
												<tr>
													<td class="fontNormal">
														<p class="textNormal">NASSCOM encourages State Governments / Colleges / 
															Universities / Training Institutes across the country to commit to this program 
															by conducting NAC for their students. With this, they will also be able to 
															align their employment initiatives with NAC.
															<br>
															<br>
															We envisage that, with active participation from all the stakeholders, NAC will 
															immensely help the industry as well as the society at large as this has been 
															designed and developed after due deliberation and support from all industry 
															players. Some immediate benefits, which all stakeholders can collectively look 
															forward to, are as follows:
														</p>
